<div class="container">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
    <h1><%= @accommodation.title %></h1>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <a href="#">Share</a> |
      <a href="#">Save</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex">
      <%= image_tag "pic1.jpg", alt: "", class: 'w-50 object-fit-cover' %>

    <div class="w-50">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
          <%= image_tag "pic2.jpg", alt: "", class: 'd-block w-100 h-100' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <%= image_tag "pic3.jpg", alt: "", class: 'd-block w-100 h-100' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
          <%= image_tag "pic4.jpg", alt: "", class: 'd-block w-100 h-100' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <%= image_tag "pic5.jpg", alt: "", class: 'd-block w-100 h-100' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8">
      <div>
        <h2>Accommodation summary</h2>
          <ul style="list-style: none">
              <li>Type of place: <%= @accommodation.type_of_place %></li>
              <li><%= @accommodation.bedroom_count %> bedrooms</li>
              <li><%= @accommodation.bed_count %> beds</li>
              <li><%= @accommodation.bathroom_count %> bathrooms</li>
              <li>Rating: <%= @accommodation.rating %> stars</li>
          </ul>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="d-flex flex-row">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-6">
            <p>Link to host's profile</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <p>Hosted by <%= @accommodation.host_name %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h4>Designed for staying cool</h4>
        <p>Beat the heat with the A/C and ceiling fan.</p>
        <h4>Self check-in</h4>
        <p>Check yourself in with the smartlock.</p>
        <h4>Free cancellation before 6 Dec</h4>
        <p>Get a full refund if you change your mind.</p>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed suscipit lacus nec ligula molestie, eget egestas arcu commodo. Phasellus sit amet augue sit amet magna dignissim porttitor. Pellentesque eu turpis nec nunc accumsan iaculis.</p>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2>Where you'll sleep</h2>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2>What this place offers</h2>
        <ul>
          <% @accommodation.amenities.each do |amenity| %>
            <li><%= amenity.name %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#" role="button">Show more amenities</a>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2>Calendar</h2>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2><%= @accommodation.rating %> stars, <%= Review.all.length %> reviews</h2>

      </div>

      <hr>



      <div class="list-group d-flex flex-row flex-wrap">
        <ul>
          <% @accommodation.reviews.each do |review|%>
              <%= review.content %>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#" role="button">Show more reviews</a>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2>Where you'll be</h2>
        <p>Insert map here</p>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div>
        <h2>Meet your host</h2>
        <%= @accommodation.host_name %>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <div class="row">
        <h2>Things to know</h2>
          <div class="col-4">
            <h3>House rules</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Check-in after 3:00pm</li>
                <li>Check-out before 11:00am</li>
                <li>4 guests maximum</li>
              </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="col-4">
            <h3>Safety and property</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Check-in after 3:00pm</li>
                <li>Check-out before 11:00am</li>
                <li>4 guests maximum</li>
              </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="col-4">
            <h3>Cancellation policy</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Check-in after 3:00pm</li>
                <li>Check-out before 11:00am</li>
                <li>4 guests maximum</li>
              </ul>
          </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="bg-white rounded shadow p-3">
        <h2>$62 SGD night</h2>
        <%# <input type="text" data-controller="datepicker"> %>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-3">
          <p>Check-in</p>
          <p>Check-out</p>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex p-3">
          <p>Guest dropdown button</p>
        </div>

        <div class="d-grid mx-auto">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-border-radius" type="button">Reserve</button>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center p-3">You won't be charged yet</p>


        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-3">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>$62 SGD x 5 nights</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>$310 SGD</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>Cleaning fee</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>$15 SGD</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>Airbnb service fee</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <p>$58 SGD</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>


        <hr>

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-3">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
              <p></strong>Total before taxes</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6">
              <p>$383 SGD</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>


      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
